Product Description (Plain Text):
Old Glory has a blend of clear and red petite glass crystals, with stars printed on a navy blue barrel, silver hardware, and a red gem on top.You can purchase the pen alone, or bundle the pen with the Pippin Flag pin.Your pen will come with black ink installed and an extra refill cartridge

